*
 * @desc Creates safe type tuple.
 * @example
 * const expected = ['Barkley', 'Rosser']
 *     , StringPair = SafeTupleBuilder.of(String, String)
 *     , name = new StringPair(...expected)
 *     , [first, last] = name.getAll();
 *
 *    first // Barkley
 *    last // Rosser
 *
 *    name.unpack((first, last) => {
 *      first // Barkley
 *      last // Rosser
 *    });
 *
 *    name.get(0); // Barkley
 *    name.get(1) // Rosser
 *
